# Title: Defrag Deactivation
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), Bartlomiej Czyz (@bczyz1)
# Date: 2019-03-04
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects the deactivation and disabling of the Scheduled defragmentation task as seen by Slingshot APT group
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.execution, attack.persistence, attack.t1053.005, attack.s0111, detection.emerging-threats

CommandLine IN ("*/delete*", "*/change*") CommandLine="*/TN*" CommandLine="*\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Defrag\\ScheduledDefrag*" Image="*\\schtasks.exe"